SP.P:
Your delicacy carries you too far. In this I confer a favour on myself: however, we'll talk no more on the subject at present—Let us walk towards the house;


our friends will depart else without my bidding them adieu.
Exeunt.

And Hodge—




AIR.

Hodge.



Well, well, say no more;

Sure you told me before;

I see the full length of my tether;

Do you think I'm a fool,

That I need go to school▪

I can spell you and put you together.




A word to the wise

Will always suffice;

Addsniggers, go talk to your parrot;

I'm not such an elf,

Tho' I say it myself,

But I know a sheep's head from a carrot.
Exit.

